column3: The high velocity web framework for Java and Scala.  Similar to a less bloated Rails or a more feature complete Sinatra I guess
Activate is a framework to persist objects in Scala. It is a STM (Software Transactional Memory) distributed and durable with pluggable persistence.

AutoJS is a library to continuously autocomplete textarea based on a standard dictionary. Dictionary has been deviced based on researches and linguistic methods, keeping an eye on minimizing the size of the library. Complete project is written in plain js, with no external dependencies

Check your DNS against over 1500 global DNS servers

DNSYO is a little tool I built to help me keep track of DNS propagation.

In short, it's nslookup, if nslookup queried over 1500 servers and collated their results.

The Dumbster is a very simple fake SMTP server designed for unit and system testing applications that send email messages. It responds to all standard SMTP commands but does not deliver messages to the user.

giter8 or g8 is a command line tool for applying templates

jBCrypt is a Java implementation of OpenBSD's Blowfish password hashing code, as described in A Future-Adaptable Password Scheme by Niels Provos and David Mazières.
Natural date parsing
JDBC connector for connecting/creating SQLite databases

jQuery in Java.

Jerry is a fast and concise Java Library that simplifies HTML document parsing traversing and manipulating. Jerry is designed to change the way that you parse HTML content.
Jexmec is a clean, simple, non-intrusive library supporting plugin based development on the Java platform.
Handle console and cli input
Joda-Money provides a library of classes to store amounts of money or currency.

Jodd is an open-source Java utility library and set of micro frameworks. Jodd tools enriches JDK with many powerful and feature rich utilities. It helps with everyday task makes code more robust and reliable. Jodd frameworks is set of lightweight application frameworks, compact yet powerful. Designed following the CoC, DRY and SCS principles, it makes development simple, but not simpler; you get 90% of the features with 10% of usual effort
The kraken suite is a secure and scalable layer that extends express by providing structure and convention.
Customizable and extensible toolkit for transforming lightweight text markup into various types of output formats, written in Scala.

Liberator is a Clojure library that helps you expose your data as resources while automatically complying with all the relevant requirements of the HTTP specification (RFC-2616). Your resources will automatically gain useful HTTP features, such as caching and content negotiation. Liberator was inspired by Erlang’s Webmachine. By following the constraints and requirements in RFC-2616, liberator will enable you to create application according to a REST architecture.
A simple tool to transform sources to markdown for generating documentation

MemSQL is the highest performing in-memory database that accelerates applications provides real-time analytics and combines structured and semi-structured data into a consolidated Big Data solution. MemSQL empowers organizations to make data-driven decisions better engage customers and discover competitive advantages.
Scala Migrations is a library to manage upgrades and rollbacks to database schemas.
Neo4j is a robust (fully ACID) transactional property graph database. Due to its graph data model, Neo4j is highly agile and blazing fast.
A fresh approach to JSON loading that speeds up web applications by providing the parsed objects before the response completes.
An open source tool set for building web applications in Clojure
An sbt plugin for building Scala Web applications
Template based DOM manipulation
Java API to obtain artefacts from a repository system
A type-safe REST client for Android and Java from Square

Riemann aggregates events from your servers and applications with a powerful stream processing language. Send an email for every exception raised by your code. Track the latency distribution of your web app. See the top processes on any host, by memory and CPU. Combine statistics from every Riak node in your cluster and forward to Graphite. Send alerts when a key process fails to check in. Know how many users signed up right this second.

Riemann provides low-latency, transient shared state for systems with many moving parts.
Ultra small MVP framework

The ScalaUtils library is focused on constructs related to quality that are useful in both production code and tests. Although ScalaTest is tightly integrated with ScalaUtils, you can use ScalaUtils with any Scala project and any test framework. The ScalaUtils library has no dependencies other than Scala itself.

Lightning-fast Scala collections framework

    import scala.collection.par._
    import Scheduler.Implicits.global

    (0 until 15000000).toPar.reduce(_ + _)

ScalikeJDBC is a tidy SQL-based DB access library for Scala developers. This library naturally wraps JDBC APIs and provides you easy-to-use APIs. ScalikeJDBC is a practical and production-ready one. Use this library for your real projects.
Tiny dependency resolver.  Maven backed unmanaged lib downloader thingy
An embedded Scala web server powered by Netty networking and Akka processing.
Spark is a simple web framework for java
A Scala ORM and DSL for talking with Databases with minimum verbosity and maximum type safety
SSH client for Java
Dependencies as types. Using types for immutable package management. Because we want a static insurance, i.e. to know everything we need about dependencies in compile time.
Queue related classes like the FileBackedQueue class and simple thing like that
Lazy collection support a la Clojure for Java
Small components for building apps, manipulating data, and automating a distributed infrastructure.
The Trove library provides high speed regular and primitive collections for Java.

Undertow is a flexible performant web server written in java, providing both blocking and non-blocking API’s based on NIO.

Undertow has a composition based architecture that allows you to build a web server by combining small single purpose handlers. The gives you the flexibility to choose between a full Java EE servlet 3.1 container, or a low level non-blocking handler, to anything in between.

Undertow is designed to be fully embeddable, with easy to use fluent builder APIs. Undertow’s lifecycle is completely controlled by the embeding application.

Undertow is sponsored by JBoss and is the default web server in the Wildfly Application Server.
Unix commands for Java including grep and what not
